  "description": "<p>Go exploring without spending your entire budget on gear. The best-selling Centaurus line uses quick-drying synthetic insulation for both value and reliable performance. Designed with thoughtful touches and a little extra room, this wide sleeping bag lets you stretch out at night, but keeps your pack slim and light on the hike in. There's a zippered pocket on the draft tube, a 3/4-length zip and 2 loops that let you hang it up to air out.</p><ul><li>Insulated with synthetic HyperLoft that contains recycled fibres</li><li>Outer shell fabric is Pertex Quantum nylon with a DWR treatment to shed moisture. Lining is nylon</li><li>Wide cut gives you room to sprawl, but still provides thermal efficiency</li><li>Hood drawcord is operable with one hand</li><li>Pocket on the draft tube has an invisible zipper and fits glasses or a headlamp</li><li>3/4-length YKK\u00ae zipper helps trim the weight</li><li>2 hanging loops on the foot end</li><li>Includes a stuff sack and a home storage bag</li></ul>",
